reviewText:
two of the movies cut off before I could see the end...very disappointing
(penny serenade and fathers little dividend)
Came with all the movies and packaged real nice. Like it a lot.
Irene Dunne, is my #1 all-time favorite actress of her era. I love the way she interacts with the other actors/actresses. I love this movie so much!
I think that this is a great buy. For a very small price they are giving you 5 great very difficult to find classics. This is a collection that you will cherish if you like classics.
This will make you an Irene Dunne lover!  The only one I did not like was Jane Eyre as no one played the lead better than Joan Fontaine ... but the other movies are just great.
